   _language="" /%}

{% horizontalSplit noHeader=false _language="" %}
{% sectionHeader color="blue" title="Find your stop" icon="" _language="" /%}

{% bodySection
   centered=false
   width="default"
   color="blue"
   textSize="medium"
   _language="" %}
From April through November, the Plan C Community Road Trip will travel across all 50 states, Puerto Rico, and Guam, partnering with grassroots organizers, artists, advocates, students, mutual aid groups, and local communities to create spaces for connection, education, and action around abortion access and reproductive freedom.

Every stop is shaped by the communities hosting it, making each event unique, locally grounded, and reflective of the people leading the work on the ground.
{% /bodySection %}
